# Railway Deployment Configuration
# This file contains all necessary configurations for Railway deployment

## Required Environment Variables (set in Railway Dashboard)
GROQ_API_KEY=your-groq-api-key-here
MODEL=mixtral-8x7b-32768
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
ENVIRONMENT=production

## Optional Variables
AGENT_TIMEOUT=30
PORT=8000
PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1

## PostgreSQL Configuration (if using Railway PostgreSQL service)
DB_HOST=postgres
DB_PORT=5432
DB_USER=admin
DB_PASSWORD=your-secure-password
DB_NAME=p2pdb

## Notes
# - PORT will be automatically assigned by Railway and overrides default 8000
# - PYTHONUNBUFFERED ensures immediate logging to stdout
# - Set GROQ_API_KEY to your actual API key in Railway Dashboard
# - All variables can be set in Railway UI: Service Settings → Variables
